        <p>Positioned for analysis support, commentary, review, and repeatable spreadsheet operations.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
        <span>02</span>
        <h2>Everyday productivity</h2>
        <p>Useful for cleanup, reporting, validation, documentation, and workbook handoff habits.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
        <span>03</span>
        <h2>Templates and guides</h2>
        <p>Structured around reusable assets and practical how-to content, not a thin utility directory.</p>
    </article>
</section>
